Text.val: Ophalen product aan de hand van PPR_ID

SQL_STMT_U.val: select ppr.ppr_relatienummer "RELATIENR", ppr.ppr_productnummer "PRODUCTNR", ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product "PRODUCT_VOLGNR", p.PR_ID "PR_ID", c.CL_RELATIE_TYPE "CL_RELATIE_TYPE", nvl(rh.EOR_KENMERK_ID,0)"EOR_KENMERK_ID" , ld.lety_id "LETY_ID" from producten_per_relatie ppr inner join producten p on p.pr_productnummer=ppr.ppr_productnummer inner join clienten c on cl_nummer=ppr.ppr_relatienummer left outer join holders_per_product h on h.hpp_relatienummer=ppr.ppr_relatienummer and h.hpp_product=ppr.ppr_productnummer and h.hpp_product_volgnr=ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product and h.hpp_type_holder=1 left outer join rekeninghouders_details rh on rh.eor_partij_id=h.hpp_holdernummer left outer join legalentity_details ld on ld.party_id = h.hpp_holdernummer where ppr.ppr_id=~1

Comment.val: /* Per deduction Id and for all parties under the product (ppr_id). If only one party under the product is not Tax Exempt then alle the tax calculationlines should be returned to the request */

Text.val: When all holders are exempted of paying tax, no calculation is necessary, but it's desirable
to be able to report the base-amount anyways. In order to do that a fixed 100% deduction discount
tariff is linked to the deduction :
If really used. a subtask to find the exact tariff for a special year exist should be implemented.
For now we only support flat Tariffs

SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from holders_per_product h where h.hpp_relatienummer = ~1 and h.hpp_product = ~2 and h.hpp_product_volgnr = ~3 and h.hpp_type_holder in (1, 2) and (exists (select 1 from RM_PARTIJ_TAX_CHARACTERISTICS rtc inner join country_deductions cd on cd.country_id = rtc.ptch_land_nummer and rtc.ptch_belastingplichtig = 'J' and cd.has_exemption = 1 where h.hpp_holdernummer = rtc.ptch_eor_partij_id) or exists (select 1 from party_deductions pd where pd.party_id = h.hpp_holdernummer and pd.has_exemption = 1 ) or exists (select 1 from special_ca_tax_exclusions s where s.party_id = h.hpp_holdernummer))

select count(*) from holders_per_product h where h.hpp_relatienummer = ~1 and h.hpp_product = ~2 and h.hpp_product_volgnr = ~3 and h.hpp_type_holder in (1, 2) and not (exists (select 1 from RM_PARTIJ_TAX_CHARACTERISTICS rtc inner join country_deductions cd on cd.country_id = rtc.ptch_land_nummer and rtc.ptch_belastingplichtig = 'J' and cd.has_exemption = 1 and cd.deduction_id = ~4 where h.hpp_holdernummer = rtc.ptch_eor_partij_id ) or exists (select 1 from party_deductions pd where pd.party_id = h.hpp_holdernummer and pd.has_exemption = 1 and pd.deduction_id = ~4 ) or exists ( select 1 from special_ca_tax_exclusions s where s.party_id = h.hpp_holdernummer and s.dedu_id = ~4
))
